    "MissionGiver": "Eckhart Security",
    "Title": "Client's Cargo Needs Recovering",
    "Description": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Recover Cargo\nApproval code: = ~mission(ApprovalCode)\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nClient's cargo was mid-transport when they ran into some ship trouble, and now a group of opportunistic outlaws are looking to cash in on this.\n\nIf you accept, head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and deal with the outlaws guarding the cargo. Extract it using a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>, recover the cargo, load it in to a ship that can transport <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4>, and deposit it on the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
    "DisplayDescription": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Recover Cargo\nApproval code: = [ApprovalCode]\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nClient's cargo was mid-transport when they ran into some ship trouble, and now a group of opportunistic outlaws are looking to cash in on this.\n\nIf you accept, head to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> and deal with the outlaws guarding the cargo. Extract it using a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>, recover the cargo, load it in to a ship that can transport <EM4>32 SCU cargo containers</EM4>, and deposit it on the freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
